is distributed only in South America, occurring from southern 
<collectingCountry box="[239,314,1211,1235]" name="Brazil" pageId="23" pageNumber="22">Brazil</collectingCountry>
to northern 
<collectingCountry box="[463,591,1211,1235]" name="Argentina" pageId="23" pageNumber="22">Argentina</collectingCountry>
. The specimens listed below from Amazonas and Pará states represent NEW RECORDS from the Brazilian Amazon.
</paragraph>
